name: Woocommerce Global
query: SELECT `tabSales Order`.`customer`, `tabAddress`.`country`, `tabSales Order`.`transaction_date` as `Order Date`, `tabSales Order`.`base_grand_total` as `Total` FROM `tabSales Order` RIGHT JOIN `tabAddress` ON `tabSales Order`.`customer_address` = `tabAddress`.`name` WHERE `tabSales Order`.`docstatus` = 1
